Type "promptarena init my-iot-demo --template community/iot-maintenance-demo"
Enter
Sleep 2s
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 4s

# === SECTION 2: Inspect Configuration ===
Hide
Type "cd my-demo-project && clear"
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Show

Type "# 2Ô∏è‚É£  Inspect your prompt configuration"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "promptarena config-inspect"
Enter
Sleep 4s

# === SECTION 3: Run a Test Scenario ===
Hide
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Show

Type "# 3Ô∏è‚É£  Run automated multi-turn test scenarios"
