Hide
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Show

Type "# 5Ô∏è‚É£  Drill into conversation details"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "cd out"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "promptarena view"
Enter
